        How to Read Your Agent's Campaign Report in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A weekly campaign report tells you more than your agent's summary. Here is what each number means, what it tells you about how the campaign is actually performing, and what to ask when the results are mixed.
      </p>
